There is budget.  I’m getting details on that.  They were due to deliver *yesterday* but aren’t feeling too much heat.  <@U02E3CRMA> has a better grip on the nitty gritty and is planning to check it out tomorrow since he’s already scheduled to be at ADX
<@U02E3CRMA> im following up with matt, thanksing him for his time etc.  i’ll wait for you to confirm here that your schedule is cool to go to adx around 9 tomorrow to get more info

also <@U026NB2U2> it’s worth noting that ADX gets these kinds of requests all the time but declines cuz it’s not in their wheelhouse or it’s not core to their business.  They’d be open to strategic partnerships.  Admittedly, these project would be smaller budgets but definitely good for community building, could be fun and could be good ‘filler’ between larger projects.
